## 2. Stat cards вЂ” `GET /app/attendance/summary`

The four cards at the top of the screen. No params.

```jsonc
{
В В "success": true,
В В "data": {
В В В В "hours_this_week": { "worked": 0, "target": 8 }, // Hours This Week: 0 / 8h
В В В В "attendance_rate": 100,В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В  // Attendance Rate: 100%
В В В В "late_arrivals": 0,В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В  // Late Arrivals: 0
В В В В "duty_days": { "present": 1, "total": 1 }В В В В В В В В В  // Duty Days: 1 / 1d
В В }
}
```

- **hours_this_week** вЂ” `worked` hours so far this week (Monв†’today) vs the `target`
В В (scheduled working days this week Г— 8h).
- **attendance_rate** вЂ” `present / scheduled` working days **this calendar month**, as a
В В percentage (1 decimal).
- **late_arrivals** вЂ” late clock-ins **this month**.
- **duty_days** вЂ” `present` (days clocked in) of `total` scheduled working days **this month**.

Render as: `Hours This Week {worked} / {target}h`, `Attendance Rate {rate}%`,
`Late Arrivals {n} arrivals`, `Duty Days {present} / {total}d`.

