## 4. Attendance Issues tab

A team member raises an attendance issue (e.g. a missing clock-out, a medical reason),
and HR or a manager approves/rejects it. The team member sees the status and the
reply.

### 4a. Raise an issue вЂ” `POST /app/attendance/issues`

**Body**

```jsonc
{
В В "type": "missing_clock_out",В В В В В В В В В  // required, see table below
В В "date": "2026-06-22",В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В  // YYYY-MM-DD the issue is about (default: today)
В В "details": "Forgot to clock out..."В В В  // free text
}
```

**`type` values** (the dropdown):

| value | label |
| --- | --- |
| `medical_issue` | Medical Issue |
| `missing_clock_in` | Missing Clock In |
| `missing_clock_out` | Missing Clock Out |
| `late_arrival` | Late Arrival |
| `wrong_time` | Wrong Time |
| `other` | Other |

**Response** (`201`):

```jsonc
{
В В "success": true,
В В "data": {
В В В В "id": "6a3b72634f237f3e79db7253",
В В В В "code": "Q-8137",В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В  // human reference, show this
В В В В "type": "missing_clock_out",
В В В В "date": "2026-06-22",
В В В В "details": "Forgot to clock out...",
В В В В "status": "pending",В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В  // pending | approved | rejected
В В В В "hr_response": null,В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В В  // HR/Admin reply once decided
В В В В "decided_by": null,
В В В В "decided_at": null,
В В В В "created_at": "2026-06-24T06:00:03.862Z"
В В }
}
```

An invalid `type` returns `400 BAD_REQUEST` ("Invalid issue type").

### 4b. My issue log вЂ” `GET /app/attendance/issues`

**Query**: `limit` (optional, default `50`, max `100`). Newest first, same item shape as
above. Once HR/a manager decides it:

```jsonc
{
В В "id": "6a3b72634f237f3e79db7253",
В В "code": "Q-8137",
В В "type": "missing_clock_out",
В В "date": "2026-06-22",
В В "details": "Forgot to clock out...",
В В "status": "approved",
В В "hr_response": "Approved. Your clock-out has been corrected to 5:45 PM.",
В В "decided_by": "Rishabh Vishwakarma",
В В "decided_at": "2026-06-24T06:00:31.090Z",
В В "created_at": "2026-06-24T06:00:03.862Z"
}
```

Render the `Q-####` code, a status pill (`pending` / `approved` / `rejected`), the
`details`, and вЂ” when present вЂ” the `hr_response` as "Response from HR/Admin".

